/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:13618133", "experiences/2/companyWebsite": "http://www.trip.com", "experiences/2/employmentType": "Full-time", "experiences/2/jobDescription": "A proactive account manager with over 6.5 years of experience in the dynamic online travel agent (OTA) industry. Proven expertise in strategic sales negotiation, market analysis, and revenue management, with a strong record of exceeding sales targets and expanding a robust network of hotel partnerships. Leveraging a solid background in the hotel and hospitality industry with data-driven insights to drive business growth and optimize revenue performance.\n\nPortfolio Development & Management:\n- Onboard, develop, and maintain a high-quality portfolio of hotel and property products for Trip.com's fast-growing global customer base within the assigned Phuket territory.\n- Build the portfolio of local hotel partners by introducing prospective partners to Trip.com's marketplace and facilitating a seamless onboarding process.\n\nData-Driven Market Strategy:\n- Utilize unique market insights from proprietary tools and local market analytics to identify trends, optimize pricing, and ensure content competitiveness.\n- Implement strategic sales tactics that have delivered 79% year-on-year growth in room nights and 86% year-on-year revenue increases in the assigned territory.\n\nAccount Penetration & Performance Optimization:\n- Develop targeted account penetration plans to reactivate non-participating hotels, resulting in an increase in top-tier hotel portfolios at the city level.\n- Drive hotels’ performance progression through data-driven recommendations, resulting in active hotel partners consistently participating in marketing campaigns.\n\nTraining & Consulting:\n- Conduct comprehensive training sessions for hotel partners on using extranet systems for rates, availability, promotions, reservations, content management, guest reviews, analytics, and ranking booster tools. Achieve a 78% weekly active utilization rate of the extranet system among key hotels, enhancing operational efficiency and productivity, dedicating approximately 30% of travel time to market visits.", "experiences/2/jobEndedOn": "7-2024", "experiences/2/jobLocation": "ภูเก็ต, ประเทศไทย", "experiences/2/jobLocationCountry": "SG", "experiences/2/jobStartedOn": "2-2018", "experiences/2/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/2/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/C560BAQGEVkhKVDRxcQ/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1649236016007/trip_com_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=FAuP5ejx3bSzCAPzZORuXgdGsvtLkpMGL8zt-A7gt8Y", "experiences/2/title": "Market Manager", "experiences/3/companyId": "6639912", "experiences/3/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/3/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/msocialphuket/", "experiences/3/companyName": "Millennium Resort Patong Phuket", "experiences/3/companySize": "201-500", "experiences/3/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:6639912", "experiences/3/companyWebsite": "http://www.millenniumhotels.com/millenniumpatongphuket/", "experiences/3/jobDescription": "Market Analysis & Lead Generation:\nAnalyze local market trends and competitor activity to identify new business leads.\n\nAccount Development & Relationship Management:\nDevelop new customer accounts—including travel agents, local DMCs, and corporates across Chinese, Taiwanese, Korean, Russian, Singaporean, Malaysian, and Iranian markets—and maintain strong relationships with existing partners through periodic visits and proactive communication.\n\nNegotiation & Revenue Management:\nNegotiate room rates and packages with corporate clients, applying revenue management techniques to enhance financial performance and secure profitable deals.\n\nContract Management & Strategic Collaboration:\nPrepare company contracts in line with current business and pricing conditions, work within established strategies to recognize opportunities, and collaborate with internal departments to deliver an exceptional guest experience.\n\nReporting, Customer Service & Events:\nProduce accurate, timely reports for senior management; promptly address customer queries; attend sales events and trade shows; and conduct hotel inspections for corporate representatives, travel agents, local DMCs, and familiarization groups.", "experiences/3/jobEndedOn": "2-2018", "experiences/3/jobLocation": "Center of Patong Beach Area (Connecting to Jungceylon Shopping Mall)", "experiences/3/jobLocationCountry": "TH", "experiences/3/jobStartedOn": "3-2017", "experiences/3/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/3/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D560BAQHv0TGwjnm8Fw/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1688361966020/millenniumpatong_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=tzQznYkpfFC_Nbtr5Rqj0XHwPDlgezQxutDb6GmJ6xA", "experiences/3/title": "Sales Manager", "experiences/4/companyId": "6639912", "experiences/4/companyIndustry": "Hospitality", "experiences/4/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/msocialphuket/", "experiences/4/companyName": "Millennium Resort Patong Phuket", "experiences/4/companySize": "201-500", "experiences/4/companyUrn": "urn:li:fsd_company:6639912", "experiences/4/companyWebsite": "http://www.millenniumhotels.com/millenniumpatongphuket/", "experiences/4/jobEndedOn": "3-2017", "experiences/4/jobLocation": "Center of Patong Beach Area (Connecting to Jungceylon Shopping Mall)", "experiences/4/jobLocationCountry": "TH", "experiences/4/jobStartedOn": "7-2015", "experiences/4/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/4/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D560BAQHv0TGwjnm8Fw/company-logo_400_400/company-logo_400_400/0/1688361966020/millenniumpatong_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=tzQznYkpfFC_Nbtr5Rqj0XHwPDlgezQxutDb6GmJ6xA", "experiences/4/title": "Assistant Sales Manager", "experiences/5/companyId": "1393", "experiences/5/companyIndustry": "Food and Beverage Services", "experiences/5/companyLink1": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/nestle-s-a-/", "experiences/5/