and is always smiling.\n\nA pleasure to work with and would highly recommend to any prospective employer.\n\nRgds \n", "recommendations/18/name": "Kimchhe Lork (Kim)", "recommendations/18/subtitle": "Duty Manager at Sokha Beach Resort", "recommendations/18/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kimchhe-lork-kim-89b05297/", "recommendations/18/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABR5V3cBibwhwZRUHtKHCYWFIDvNNxgHLig", "recommendations/19/context": "David Richard worked with Colin on the same team", "recommendations/19/date": "April 14, 2019", "recommendations/19/description": "Colin and I have worked together for various companies where he has been a consultant and also hired me.\nWithout doubt the best trainer that I have seen.\nHis philosophy to training is coach, listen, mentor and insure that the team are enjoying it.\nHe is exceptionally proactive and hands on. Will get the weakest team members out of their shell and boost their confidence like no other trainer I have worked with.\nHighly recommended and will continue to work with.\n", "recommendations/19/name": "Colin Q.", "recommendations/19/subtitle": "Global L&D Director | Leadership Development & Psychology of Service | Behavioural Change | Luxury Hospitality", "recommendations/19/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/colin-q-9667a037/", "recommendations/19/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAfE814BxMOMNeJ-GzwmFRKN9jVsTt9nEiI", "recommendations/20/context": "David Richard managed Eric  directly", "recommendations/20/date": "April 14, 2019", "recommendations/20/description": "Eric is one of the most talented  Chefs' that I have ever had the pleasure of working with. \nSolid, exceptionally hard working, never takes no as an answer and will always find a solution to any challenge. \nHeadstrong in a positive way and always looking to improve.\nWould be more than happy to work with him again.\n", "recommendations/20/name": "Eric  Lecras", "recommendations/20/subtitle": "Executive Holistic Wellness Chef & Culinary Director | Plant-Based & Longevity Nutrition | Founder of Thalassa Nutrition | 25 Years across Asia & the Middle East", "recommendations/20/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/eric-lecras-17332622/", "recommendations/20/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAASsz2cB1i0sTdLZ9rCw3mhuSjikBBmhj08", "recommendations/21/context": "David Richard was senior to Iwen but didn't manage Iwen directly", "recommendations/21/date": "April 14, 2019", "recommendations/21/description": "Wiwin worked for me as one of my key people at reception. Outgoing, friendly, hard working and fantastic with customers. Always dependable and she insured that everything was done before she left her shift. I have no hesitation in recommending Wiwin and would gladly work with her again", "recommendations/21/name": "Iwen Winarsih", "recommendations/21/subtitle": "Sales Manager", "recommendations/21/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/iwen-winarsih-614a11a1/", "recommendations/21/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABWvYzABJkbYTcf3UVGkO3N9zlQbfnZMMck", "recommendations/22/context": "David Richard managed Christina directly", "recommendations/22/date": "April 14, 2019", "recommendations/22/description": "Christina is one of the most talented revenue/e-commerce managers that I have had the pleasure of working with. Solid, exceptionally hard working, never takes no as an answer and will always find a solution to any challenge. \nShe is not afraid of speaking out if she disagrees with a decision. She will look at a situation/issue from all angles to insure the correct decision is made. She is in a nut shell - the ultimate revenue manager and one that I would gladly hire and work with again.", "recommendations/22/name": "Christina Lee 李慧秦", "recommendations/22/subtitle": "Assistant Director of Sales & Marketing", "recommendations/22/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/christina-lee-李慧秦-43281992/", "recommendations/22/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABOy0CYByOC6EVzR84Pbb8DzbhU99AHmOEI", "recommendations/23/context": "David Richard managed Kimpsey Fernandez directly", "recommendations/23/date": "March 3, 2019", "recommendations/23/description": "Kim worked for me at Sokha Beach Resort, Cambodia. He started as the FOM and I promoted him to RDM.  \nHe was i/c of a very large team inclusive of front office, reservations, concierge, kiosk. His operation has him in charge of 975 rooms, spread over 4 hotel/units and 2 reception areas.\n\nExceptionally detailed, very strong work ethic, will work all hours, never leaves something undone, team player, smart, excellent customer contact and highly professional. Kim has that wonderful outlook on life that no matter how difficult a situation a solution will be found. Never one to get perturbed he was always a beacon for guests and staff alike to talk to.\nI have no hesitation in recommending Kim for any role in the industry and will gladly work with him again.\n\n", "recommendations/23/name": "Kimpsey Fernandez Icalla", "recommendations/23/subtitle": ".", "recommendations/23/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kimpsey-fernandez-icalla-0b021658/", "recommendations/23/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAwiUgQBxJ9FOVjKaZmw9KwcI3Etqz5yv4g", "recommendations/24/context": "David Richard managed Fredy directly", "recommendations/24/date": "March 2, 2019", "recommendations/24/description": "Vynes was truly inspirational to work with. A work alcoholic who could see trends in the market place before anyone else. Her contribution to the operational and fiscal success of the hotel was clear to all who worked with her. Highly articulate, well groomed and an all round hotel professional. Vynes is every GM's dream of a DOSM who will be continually coming up with new ideas/promotions/campaigns to promote, market and sell the property. I have no hesitation in recommending Vynes and would gladly work with her again - David", "recommendations/24/name": "Fredy Yap 葉沛妤", "recommendations/24/subtitle": "Director Of Sales & Marketing at Xihu Resort Hotel", "recommendations/24/url": "https://www.l