ith SBI.\n\nWithout doubt one of the most talented and customer focused hoteliers in the region. Always willing and able to find a solution to all the challenges that the industry throws at us. His enthusiasm for the job is second to none. He has a deep knowledge and understanding of revenue management, thus enabling him to bring this skill to new Practitioners of the art.  His approach to all who worked with him wants Yudha to reach the pinnacle of our profession.\n", "recommendations/32/name": "YUDHA PRANOTO", "recommendations/32/subtitle": "Hotel Manager at Fave Diponegoro Semarang - PreOp Team", "recommendations/32/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/yudha-pranoto-9110b938/", "recommendations/32/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAfYfN0BlR4FaJR7tJe5yhIy6IbqtnmvSv0", "recommendations/33/context": "David Richard worked with Murat on the same team", "recommendations/33/date": "October 1, 2014", "recommendations/33/description": "Murat was an inspiration to work with. Could see trends in the market place before anyone else. His contribution to the operational and fiscal success of the hotel was clear to all who worked with him. Highly articulate, well groomed and an all round hotel professional.", "recommendations/33/name": "Murat Köni", "recommendations/33/subtitle": ". - .", "recommendations/33/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/murat-köni-482a1527/", "recommendations/33/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAWq3WIBiJ6dZ7DnBRLAj-L8uFZ9iAixh3c", "recommendations/34/context": "David Richard managed Christina directly", "recommendations/34/date": "October 1, 2014", "recommendations/34/description": "Lia has reported directly to me in 2 different properties for Swiss-Belhotels International in Indonesia. \nShe is extremely smart, conscientious, diligent, hard working and profoundly honest. Always fast to understand a new idea and carry it forward. \nHighly professional even in the most trying of challenges, a big smile with a 'Can Do' attitude.\nWill definitely recommend her to any future and prospective employer.\n\nDO'H ", "recommendations/34/name": "Christina Sefliana", "recommendations/34/subtitle": "Passionate Personal Assistant and HR Generalist", "recommendations/34/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/christina-sefliana-2a750a44/", "recommendations/34/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAlUgR8BuFPRxrNqxbk6ZbgcBUFef7bBKFI", "recommendations/35/context": "David Richard managed Satria directly", "recommendations/35/date": "April 24, 2014", "recommendations/35/description": "I have worked with Satria for over 3 years. In that time he has attained Ex-Housekeeper of the Year twice for the Swiss-Belhotel Group. He is a detailed, organized, dedicated and calm individual. No task was ever beyond him. He is that rare breed of housekeeper who never loses it... his calm and measured approach was always a reminder to others on how to get the job done. I have no hesitation in recommending Satria and would gladly work with him again.", "recommendations/35/name": "Satria .", "recommendations/35/subtitle": "RDM di Cambridge Hotel Medan", "recommendations/35/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/satria-13601b62/", "recommendations/35/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA0sO_oBDJU1ZDhtGi0WZX7XUs3f2pgNsOE", "recommendations/36/context": "David Richard managed Sutiono directly", "recommendations/36/date": "January 23, 2014", "recommendations/36/description": "Tio has been always a great listener and understands both sides before he actions.Extremely organized and talented at getting the best out of people. He has been a good friend & colleague. He keeps his cool and does not show emotion under pressure. To describe him in one word I would say 'Professional' and have no hesitation in recommending him to any prospective employer or client.", "recommendations/36/name": "Sutiono Sedeli", "recommendations/36/subtitle": "Human Resources Excellence Specialist", "recommendations/36/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/sutiono-sedeli-bb806831/", "recommendations/36/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAaX8rwBgp7YLk6kidWsXHpaJ4WGkPeimoM", "recommendations/37/context": "David Richard managed Muhammad directly", "recommendations/37/date": "September 5, 2013", "recommendations/37/description": "I had the privilege of working with Shafiq at the multi award winning Avari Lahore. Shafiq is an individual who can be relied upon to do a excellent job, giving a 110% commitment at all times. He is that rare breed of chef  who is very comfortable both front and back of house. Outstanding character and a pleasure to have worked with.", "recommendations/37/name": "Muhammad Shafiq", "recommendations/37/subtitle": "Executive Chef at Defence Raya Golf and Country Club", "recommendations/37/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/muhammad-shafiq-20546711/", "recommendations/37/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAJhlmUBTnU3N63e29YghEiMJpmNnFoT2lw", "recommendations/38/context": "David Richard worked with Michael on the same team", "recommendations/38/date": "August 6, 2012", "recommendations/38/description": "“I had the pleasure of working with Michael at the Royal Cliff Hotels Group. When I joined in March 2007 he was the Senior Sales Manager. Due to his work ethic, diligence, integrity and utter professionalism he was promoted to Group Deputy Director Sales & Marketing of the Group. I have no hesitation in recommending Michael and wish him all the best for his continued career”", "recommendations/38/name": "Michael Swart", "recommendations/38/subtitle": "Founder @ Asia Virtual Solutions | GSA SER VPS, Backlink Lists & Link Building Tools for SEO Professionals | Trusted by 3,400+ Marketers", "recommendations/38/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/themichaelswart/", "recommendations/38/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAoSsKgBQdJkwiuvRDDpscA9tRV3Pns1r54", "recommendations/39/context": "David Richard managed Dedik directly", "recommendations/39/date": "February 17, 2011", "recommendations/39/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Dedik in Samarinda for SBI. When I joined in March 2009 he was the DOSM. Due to his work ethic, diligence, integrity and utter professionalism I promoted him to EAM in early 2010. I have no hesitation in recommending Dedik and wish him all the best for his continued career with SBI", "recommendations/39/name": "Dedik Abdillah", "recommendations/39/subtitle": "General Manager at Swiss-Belhotel Pondok Indah", "recommendations/39/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/dedik-abdillah-567b7b22/", "recommendations/39/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAATM6F8BWPw89f0V-WH_BqPv4-yYBATChLo", "recommendations/40/context": "David Richard worked with Hartmut on the same team", "recommendations/40/date": "October 4, 2010", "recommendations/40/description": "I had the pleasure of working with Hartmut twice - Colombo, Sri Lanka and Istanbul, Turkey.\n\nWithout doubt one of the most professional and honest hoteliers in the industry. His enthuasim for the job is second to none. His direct and understanding approach to guests and staff alike will always be remembered by all those who worked with him.\n\nIn a nutshell - a 'professional hotelier who loves his job'", "recommendations/40/name": "Hartmut Noack", "recommendations/40/subtitle": "EX . Cluster General Manager Avari Hotel Lahore Pakistan,", "recommendations/40/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/hartmut-noack-6955b618/", "recommendations/40/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAOl41EBqXIaNkxsNA7MTm9qh9KDM5XRfkQ", "recommendations/41/context": "David Richard worked with Hakan on the same team", "recommendations/41/date": "October 19, 2007", "recommendations/41/description": "Organised and structured individual. Would highly recommend.", "recommendations/41/name": "Hakan Besnili", "recommendations/41/subtitle": "General Manager", "recommendations/41/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/hakanbesnili/", "recommendations/41/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAADqOWUBxlBwC1afb51-A2nUIKiK7Xx1FZM", "recommendationsReceived/0/context": "Pathma worked with David Richard but they were at different