d, we achieved a lot.", "recommendationsReceived/17/name": "Kimpsey Fernandez Icalla", "recommendationsReceived/17/subtitle": ".", "recommendationsReceived/17/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kimpsey-fernandez-icalla-0b021658/", "recommendationsReceived/17/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAwiUgQBxJ9FOVjKaZmw9KwcI3Etqz5yv4g", "recommendationsReceived/18/context": "David Richard was senior to Kimchhe but didn't manage Kimchhe directly", "recommendationsReceived/18/date": "June 12, 2019", "recommendationsReceived/18/description": "Mr. David is an optimistic, energetic person and it was a great pleasure to have a chance working with him.\nHis flexible, supportive and interactive leadership style, matched with an ability to provide a clear direction, builds productive teams who feel motivated and empowered to perform well (without the need to be micro-managed). His natural ability to connect with team members at all levels results in honest and open communication, and unifies all departments to work together to achieve business aims and objectives. He is an outstanding GM everyone would wish to work with and I certainly do hope to have an opportunity to work with David again.\n", "recommendationsReceived/18/name": "Kimchhe Lork (Kim)", "recommendationsReceived/18/subtitle": "Duty Manager at Sokha Beach Resort", "recommendationsReceived/18/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/kimchhe-lork-kim-89b05297/", "recommendationsReceived/18/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABR5V3cBibwhwZRUHtKHCYWFIDvNNxgHLig", "recommendationsReceived/19/context": "Christina reported directly to David Richard", "recommendationsReceived/19/date": "April 4, 2019", "recommendationsReceived/19/description": "Mr. David is an enthusiastic person with the industry core management experience, is great and proud to be part of his team! \nHis Revenue Management skill is to develop and implement of a clear strategic plan, which he always sharing different kind of situation to advise me to think “out of the box”, 