 David who was an exceptional GM. His hands-on approach to career, motivational speaking and consulting, excellent management skill, and amazing leadership personality won him the respect of the staff. Whenever I have questions or concerns, he always responds right away with clear directions. He always advise to think “out of the box”to generate some radical ideas.. His patience made me motivated to do the best job I can. Under his leadership resort achieved the highest achievement in year 2018. He is the best GM everyone would love to work with.", "recommendationsReceived/21/name": "Fredy Yap 葉沛妤", "recommendationsReceived/21/subtitle": "Director Of Sales & Marketing at Xihu Resort Hotel", "recommendationsReceived/21/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/vyyap/", "recommendationsReceived/21/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAA72jHsBj2aIpWlCeoI0gIR5VgXpPXjQYiw", "recommendationsReceived/22/context": "David Richard was senior to Nelly but didn't manage Nelly directly", "recommendationsReceived/22/date": "May 24, 2017", "recommendationsReceived/22/description": "David was a great Leader who taught us to think creatively and innovatively. I was given an important project to handle the first Green Hotel Competition in 2013. And we did achieve the 1st hotel in Medan to receive the National Green Hotel Award for the period of 2013-2015. He believed in his team. He is a brilliant revenue professional, very objective in expressing his concerns, speaks informally to his team as if we are his best friends, full of humor and always believes in his team to do their best. He is always one step ahead of all competitors in town. It's too bad that I did not have a chance to learn revenue management from him. I really appreciated him giving me the opportunity to finish a 9 months cross training to the hotel operations that I am now fully equilled with all the knowledge to go further up the level. You are a great boss and inspiring buddy to me. I would be very delighted f there were an opportunity in the future to work with you, Sir! ", "recommendationsReceived/22/name": "Nelly Lim", "recommendationsReceived/22/subtitle": "Motivational and inspiring leader, guiding mentor and persistent coach; always brings a positive vibe to anyone around", "recommendationsReceived/22/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/nelly-lim-50994627/", "recommendationsReceived/22/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAAAWoC1kBeDcZtzSYNUuKpWuARP93RkM6QPQ", "recommendationsReceived/23/context": "Mis Mariani reported directly to David Richard", "recommendationsReceived/23/date": "July 27, 2015", "recommendationsReceived/23/description": "Great GM that I worked with ever, a very strong leadership characteristic, he  knows well that leadership style should be situational and depending on the need of the teams. Very open minded and he opens for any feedback. He also very expert in calculating and analysis of the matter at hand. And I believe he will always inspiring people to be a better leader.", "recommendationsReceived/23/name": "Mis Mariani Rakib", "recommendationsReceived/23/subtitle": "General Manager at KHAS Semarang Hotel", "recommendationsReceived/23/url": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/mis-mariani-rakib-b79019b2/", "recommendationsReceived/23/urn": "urn:li:fsd_profile:ACoAABfZ9E0BPvk7b7AZRyerrdjulapxs7dpBz0", "recommendationsReceived/24/context": "Christina worked with David Richard on the same team", "recommendationsReceived/24/date": "October 14, 2014", "recommendationsReceived/24/description": "I worked with Pak David for two properties of the Swiss-Belhotel International chain in Indonesia. His aptitude as a Leader is unquestionable. Pak David is very detail oriented on all matters which is why his hotels are so successful. He knows how to encourage his staff to think 'Out of the Box' which gives a great team effort and excellent results. \nWorking with him is an experience that has totally re-defined my career development.", "recommendationsReceived/24/name": "Christina Sefliana",